Text: Deja News Registration Confirmationto My Deja News You have registered for My Deja News using the email address If you did not register for My Deja News please ignore this message In order to use many of the Deja News personalized features such as posting and Deja Communities we must confirm your email address Having our members use confirmed email addresses allows us to minimize spam and other problems To confirm your email address visit the following Web page ecxpafdedaafcaeff If your email software supports it you can simply click on the link Since this Web page address URL is quite lengthy however you may find it necessary to copy the entire URL and paste it into your Web browser As a reminder your username is mtaylo and your password is oberon You may wish to keep this email to refer to in case you forget If you have any questions about My Deja News please refer to the Help page at helphelpregstrshtml Thanks Deja News
